ed="T" n="0806b27"/><persName key="A011306">釋清徹</persName>，未知何許人也。周遊律肆，密護根<lb
ed="T" n="0806b28"/>門，即無常師，唯善是與。初於<placeName key="PL000000057836"><placeName>吳苑</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0806b29"/><placeName>北院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011021">道恒<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，親乎閫奧<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g592"/>，深該理致，而<placeName key="PL000000018628">鐘</placeName><pb ed="T" n="0806c" xml:id="T50.2061.0806c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0806c01"/>華望<ptr type="glossary" target="#g730"/>，無不推稱。<persName key="A002120">憲宗</persName><date from-iso="+0813-02-09" key="j20180422018395" to-iso="+0814-01-28"><name>元和</name>八年癸巳</date>中，約<lb
ed="T" n="0806c02"/>志著記二十卷，亦鳩聚諸家要當之說，解<lb
ed="T" n="0806c03"/><persName key="A001519">南山</persName>鈔<ptr target="#n1290"/>，號《集義》焉，或云《後堂》<ptr target="#n1837"/>。至<date from-iso="+0815-02-17" key="j20187802019133" to-iso="+0816-02-05">十年</date>畢<lb
ed="T" n="0806c04"/>簡。今<placeName key="PL000000018628">豫章</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000026483">武昌</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000009739">晉陵</placeName>講<anchor xml:id="beg0806sgsz4"/>士<anchor xml:id="end0806sgsz4"/>多行此義。甞覽<lb
ed="T" n="0806c05"/>此記，繁廣是宗。<persName key="A011306">徹</persName>未知其終。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0806c0601"><lb
ed="T" n="0806c06"/>系曰：<persName key="A011306">徹<roleName>公</roleName></persName>言行，無乃太簡乎？通曰：「繁略有據，<lb
ed="T" n="0806c07"/>名實錄也。昔<persName key="A004022">太史公</persName>可弗欲廣<persName key="G000022">三</persName><persName key="G000026">五</persName>之世<lb
ed="T" n="0806c08"/>事耶？蓋<persName key="A002433">唐</persName><persName key="A002434">虞</persName>之前，史氏淳略，後世何述焉？今<lb
ed="T" n="0806c09"/>不遂富贍，職由此也。又與弗來赴告不書<lb
ed="T" n="0806c10"/>同也<ptr type="glossary" target="#g732"/>。諸有繁略不均，必<anchor xml:id="beg0806sgsz5"/>袪<anchor xml:id="end0806sgsz5"/><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g740"/>誚讓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g735"/>焉。」</p>
